OL,3,CMan suffers facial injuries after
OL,4,Cassault
OL,6,FA man has sustained facial injuries
OL,7,Ffollowing an assault in east Belfast.
OL,9,FThe incident occurred on Thursday.
OL,11,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "It was
OL,12,Freported at around 11.40pm that a man
OL,13,Fwas punched in the face and assaulted
OL,14,Fin the Ravenhill Road area as he lay
OL,15,Fon the ground by another male.
OL,17,F"The victim sustained facial injuries
OL,18,Fas a result of the incident, and was
OL,19,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
